title: The Flash 231-246 + All-Flash 1
description:
Leads directly from Flash: The Fastest Man Alive series and follows the return of Wally West as he struggles with trying to raise his two super powered twins, plagued by accelerated growth and their inexperience in the heroic game; a task made more difficult by Wally's unemployment, and inability to keep a steady job, and the mistrust of the League for his decision to bring two children in the fold.


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
